Crack the eggs into a microwavable bowl and season. Whisk well with a fork until completely combined and there are some bubbles on the surface. Microwave for 30 seconds then stir with a fork. Microwave again, if not cooked to your liking, in 10 second bursts until almost set. It will continue cooking a little when removed from the microwave. Stir again and set aside for 30 seconds.Butter your toast and tip the egg on top.